articles.title: Intel to receive $8.5bn in US funding for high-end chip manufacturing - Financial Times
articles.description: Preliminary agreement includes $11bn loan as company expands capacity in Arizona and other states
articles.content: Intel will receive $8.5bn in direct funding and $11bn in loans from the US government to expand its capacity to make high-end chips, as it seeks to reinvent itself as a national champion in the secto… [+3734 chars]
